Name: EARLY WARNING BEARING IN DEGREES, TRUE
DIRECTION IN DEGREES TRUE, 1 DECIMAL PLACE
Explanation: THE COURSE AND SPEED OF A VESSEL MEASURED IN DEGREES (000.0-359.9) AND KNOTS.

Name: SEMI-MAJOR AXIS ORIENTATION IN TENTHS OF DEGREES, TRUE

Name: BOATLANE AXIS IN DEGREES TRUE

Name: DISPOSITION AXIS
Explanation: THE AXIS OF THE DISPOSITION IN DEGREES TRUE.
